{
  "stem": "25423.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still remember the book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was one of these western novels written in the United States in English translated into Polish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Suddenly, four or five young Ukrainians came in and dragged me out into the street, where I was beaten and dragged into the prison.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know what-- before I knew what was happening to me, I found myself in the city prison, which was not too far-- about a block and a half away.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't touch women at the time, or children-- just men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was considered already a man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only in the prison, but first on the street, because they dragged other men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were all chasing out and beating us, you see, with rifles and all kinds of sticks and fists, and chasing us through the center of the street, not on the sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the sidewalks, you have Poles and Ukrainians clapping hands and saying-- well, enjoying this, this spectacle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this whole group was run into the prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the prison, we were chased into a corner and put to work to drag out bodies of prisoners who were executed by the NKVD.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they did is they sealed them in cellars and set the prison on fire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must be a few thousand bodies there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were doing it probably from early spring, sometimes-- yes, they must have started it sometime, in my opinion, around March, April.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they first executed the people and threw the bodies into the cellars and sealed the cellars.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
